    <summary><span data-ttu-id="86be7-101">检测到被拒绝的主机资源时引发的异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="86be7-101">The exception that is thrown when a denied host resource is detected.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="86be7-102"><xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute>基于公共语言运行时启动时所建立的主机保护首选项，使用特性来确定是否可以加载类型或成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="86be7-102">A <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute> attribute is used to determine if a type or member can be loaded, based on the host's protection preferences established when the common language runtime is started.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="86be7-103">如果调用具有活动的类型或成员 <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute> ，则该保护特性会出现链接请求。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="86be7-103">If a type or member with an active <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute> is called, a link demand occurs for that protection attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="86be7-104">如果调用方不满足主机保护的需求， <xref:System.Security.HostProtectionException> 则会引发。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="86be7-104">If the caller does not meet the demand for host protection, a <xref:System.Security.HostProtectionException> is thrown.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="86be7-105"><xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute>不是权限，即使它是链接请求的目标。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="86be7-105">A <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute> is not a permission, even though it is the target of a link demand.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="86be7-106">由于 <xref:System.Security.HostProtectionException> 链接请求引发了，因此无法对其进行处理，因此不能在代码中对其进行捕获和处理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="86be7-106">Because a <xref:System.Security.HostProtectionException> is thrown for a link demand, it cannot be handled, and therefore it cannot be trapped and processed in code.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
